long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shows the country of origin on the products page of Amazon & Ebay.

The information is gotten by scraping the information off the products page so this extension may be slow to display the country of origin on some connections. For more information see the Getting Started page.

https://luis-c465.github.io/made-in/
